******************************************************************
* If you're new to this chess scenario editor, please read these *
* instructions carefully.                                        *
*                                                                *
* Placing a chess piece format:                                  *
* [player] [chess piece] [location]                              *
*                                                                *
* Clear a square format:                                         *
* 0 [location]                                                   *
*                                                                *
* Example:                                                       *
* 1 1 A1 = Place a player 1 pawn in square A1                    *
* 0 A1 = Clear square A1                                         *
*                                                                *
* Per player you can place at most:                              *
* 8 pawns                                                        *
* 2 rooks, knights, and bishops                                  *
* 1 queen and king                                               *
*                                                                *
* When your scenario is completed, enter '0' to exit editor.     *
* You can then save your scenario in one of the three scenario   *
* files.                                                         *
*                                                                *
* I hope you enjoy this scenario editor.                         *
******************************************************************